definition: hundreds/a large number/lit. by the hundreds and thousands
to succeed/to finish/to complete/to accomplish/to become/to turn into/to be all right/OK!/one tenth
on top/upon/above/upper/previous/first (of multiple parts)/to climb/to get onto/to go up/to attend (class or university)

sentences.english: The deep connection between Sami herders and the reindeer is hundreds of years old.
sentences.chinese: 薩米牧人和馴鹿之間的深厚關係有成百上千年的歷史。

sentences.english: The character likely has hundreds or even thousands of vassals .
sentences.chinese: 人物可能擁有成百上千的奴僕。

sentences.english: We heard it at home hundreds of times, one year after another.
sentences.chinese: 我們在家裏年復一年的聽了成百上千次這個故事。

sentences.english: Further still, and we are accompanied by millions upon millions of other galaxies in the Universe.
sentences.chinese: 再遠一些，還成百上千萬的其他星系陪伴着我們。

sentences.english: Hundreds of possible brown dwarfs are out there awaiting confirmation.
sentences.chinese: 成百上千個褐矮星仍等待着確認身份。

sentences.english: There are hundreds of expressions and combinations of words using hand in the English language.
sentences.chinese: 在英語裏，有成百上千個短語和詞組跟手有關的。

sentences.english: Hundreds of characters. Thousands of monsters. The Yu-Gi-Oh!
sentences.chinese: 成百上千的人物角色和怪獸設定。

sentences.english: Hunderds of fans crowed at the entrance to see the famous singer.
sentences.chinese: 成百上千的歌迷擠在入口處想要見到那個著名的歌星。

sentences.english: Hundreds of thousands could now be seeking appointments with their doctor.
sentences.chinese: 成百上千的病人可能已經開始和醫生預約了。

sentences.english: The hour strikes and the melody of hundreds of grandfather and cuckoo clocks rings out.
sentences.chinese: 一到整點，成百上千的落地鍾和布穀鍾齊鳴。

sentences.english: Hundreds of US warp; anes are raining bombs on Iraqi targets.
sentences.chinese: 成百上千的美軍戰機把炸彈傾瀉到伊拉克目標上。

sentences.english: In the autumn，by the thousands，they come home for the winter.
sentences.chinese: 秋季，它們會成百上千地在這裏築窩，躲過嚴冬。

sentences.english: Andromeda detected hundreds of thousands of machine parts in the area.
sentences.chinese: 仙女座號探測到有成百上千的機械部件在那個區域。
會出現成百上千條搜索結果。

sentences.english: Both apps have hundreds of thousands of downloads.
sentences.chinese: 兩者都有成百上千的下載量。

sentences.english: Its members, who numbered in the hundreds, were instructed not to vote.
sentences.chinese: 它的信衆成百上千，都被指使不參與投票選舉。
